** Please be patient while the chart is being deployed **

ClickHouse can be accessed on the following DNS name from within your cluster:

    quilr-clickhouse.quilr.svc.cluster.local (port 9000)

To connect to your ClickHouse from outside the cluster execute the following commands:

    kubectl port-forward --namespace quilr svc/quilr-clickhouse 9000:9000 &

Credentials:

    echo "Username: quilradmin"
    echo "Password: $(kubectl get secret --namespace quilr quilr-clickhouse -o jsonpath="{.data.admin-password}" | base64 -d)"

